      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Good, honest car that appears to have been well cared for over time. It presents nicely overall, with a clean, attractive appearance inside and out, while still showing the light cosmetic wear, minor blemishes, and normal signs of use you\u2019d expect from a good driver-quality example. This is not a perfect or fully restored show car, but it\u2019s a solid, enjoyable vehicle that should satisfy a buyer looking for a well-kept car they can use and enjoy with confidence.",
