    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Solid good-condition car that presents well overall and should make a very usable, enjoyable driver. The exterior and interior show normal age-related wear, but nothing suggests the heavily worn condition of a project car or the flawless presentation of a mint example. It appears to have been kept up reasonably well, with the kind of cosmetic imperfections and minor signs of use you would expect from a genuinely driven, older vehicle. Buyers can expect a clean, respectable car that looks good, feels cared for, and should be suitable for regular use, while still leaving room for the next owner to address smaller details if they want to take it to the next level.",
