      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with great bones and plenty of mechanical character. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels planted, and it has the kind of driver-focused feel that makes it worth saving. Not a showroom piece, but an honest, usable platform for someone who wants a budget build, weekend toy, or parts donor with clear potential. A good opportunity to get into something interesting without spending big money.",
